title: Paul Van Dyk- Volume (seperate tracks)
description:
This is Paul Van Dyk's 3 CD greatest hits album, which also includes many brand new mixes of his older music.  The original upload was 3 gigantic fucking .mp3 files for each CD, so I got the .cue file, split it up, and I'm now putting it here for you guys!  

Bitrate:   VBR 180-250 kbps
Genre:     Trance
Artist:    Paul Van Dyk
